  "_doc": "Murders at Karlov Manor (MKM) Play + Collector recipes. Source: https://magic.wizards.com/en/news/feature/collecting-murders-at-karlov-manor . MKM was the FIRST Play Booster set: lineup is Play + Collector ONLY (no Draft Booster), so only those two types are defined and authoritative is true. Set codes: MKM = main set, TMKM = tokens, AMKM = Art Series, SPG = Special Guests (Disturbing the Scene), PLST = The List, CMKM = MKM Commander. Treatment filters reviewed against the article: MKM uses only traditional foil (no named special-foil finish like textured/raised/surge), so the foil slots correctly carry no finish filter. Serialized Ravnica City uses the serialized filter (correct); borderless dual lands + Kaya/Kellan use the borderless filter (correct); extended-art Commander/Booster Fun use extended_art (correct). Remaining approximations with no matching filter: showcase magnified / showcase dossier collapse to the showcase filter; the invisible-ink dossier (a Collector-exclusive markup on dossier mythics \u2014 no invisible_ink filter exists) stays on the showcase filter; full-art Impossible basic lands keep the basic_land filter as the load-bearing land constraint (no composite full-art+basic filter exists). The 6-7 common range is modeled as 6 fixed commons + a Special Guests/List wildcard slot reflecting the 1-in-8 (12.5%) replacement rate. [Commander-slot fix: corrected CMKM -> MKC.]",
